text: Rene Marie Russo (born February 17, 1954 Los Angeles, California) is an American movie actress. She has starred in many different types of movies. Her most notable movies include Lethal Weapon 3 (1992), Ransom (1996) and The Thomas Crown Affair (1999). ==References== Category:Actors from Burbank, California Category:American movie actors Category:1954 births Category:Living people
title: Rene Russo
